data.description: Turnkey BEAUTIFUL home near 15fwy!  New Exterior & Interior Paint, New Kitchen Cabinets, Freshly Cleaned Carpet, 3 cozy fireplaces.  Enormous Owner Suite w/fireplace large walk in closet, 3 additional spacious rooms that feature Jack & Jill bathroom upstairs.  In addition 1 full bathroom downstairs, nice size loft upstairs fun for family time along with large family room downstairs off kitchen area.  Low Maintenance front & Large backyard with sparkling pool with deck & waterfalls.  Just waiting for you to come home!
